---
---

<section class="relative py-28 overflow-hidden bg-brand-navy">

  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[900px] h-[600px] bg-brand-teal/6 rounded-full blur-[180px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[700px] h-[500px] bg-brand-navy-light/80 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.8) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[1360px] mx-auto px-8 xl:px-12">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-14">
      <p data-reveal class="eyebrow" style="color: rgba(59,169,165,0.7)">Client Feedback</p>
      <h2 data-reveal data-delay="1" class="font-heading font-bold text-white tracking-[-0.035em] leading-[1.02]" style="font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);">
        What they actually said.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Pull-quote testimonials -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

      <div data-reveal class="group relative p-9 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/8 bg-white/4 hover:bg-white/6 hover:border-white/12 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-7 right-9 font-serif text-[7rem] text-white/5 leading-none select-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-5">
          {Array(5).fill(null).map(() => (
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-brand-teal fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-white/80 text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.6] font-light tracking-[-0.01em] mb-7">
          "We'd been on the same gas contract for four years without realising it had rolled onto out-of-contract rates. Utility 1 spotted it in the first audit, renegotiated the whole thing, and we saved £28,000 in year one. Wish we'd called them sooner, honestly."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-5 border-t border-white/8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-teal/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="font-heading font-bold text-white text-sm">SC</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-white text-[14px] tracking-[-0.01em]">Sarah Chen</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-[12px]">Operations Director · National Distribution Group</p>
          </div>
          <span class="ml-auto text-brand-teal text-[11px] font-semibold bg-brand-teal/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">£28k year one</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal data-delay="2" class="group relative p-9 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/8 bg-white/4 hover:bg-white/6 hover:border-white/12 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-7 right-9 font-serif text-[7rem] text-white/5 leading-none select-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-5">
          {Array(5).fill(null).map(() => (
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-brand-teal fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-white/80 text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.6] font-light tracking-[-0.01em] mb-7">
          "Our finance team was spending a full day every month just reconciling utility invoices across 15 sites. Utility 1 got everything into one invoice. We haven't had a billing dispute since. The saving was £32k but the time saving was probably worth as much again."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-5 border-t border-white/8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-teal/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="font-heading font-bold text-white text-sm">MF</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-white text-[14px] tracking-[-0.01em]">Michael Foster</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-[12px]">Finance Manager · Sterling Facilities Ltd</p>
          </div>
          <span class="ml-auto text-brand-teal text-[11px] font-semibold bg-brand-teal/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">15 sites, £32k</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
